com.cyc.query

Interface InferenceParameters

  • All Superinterfaces:
    Cloneable, InferenceParameterGetter, InferenceParameterSetter
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    DefaultInferenceParameters, SpecifiedInferenceParameters

    public interface InferenceParameters
extends Cloneable, InferenceParameterGetter, InferenceParameterSetter

    InferenceParameters is designed to encode the parameters that can be specified for running a Cyc query.
